title: Taylor Swift won't shake it off! Singer to testify in groping case
itunes:title: Taylor Swift won't shake it off! Singer to testify in groping case
description:
Taylor Swift says she's standing up for all women who are subjected to unwelcomed groping and sexual advances by men. The singer's federal trial is underway in Denver and Swift will testify. RadarOnline's Alexis Tereszcuk and lawyer Jason Oshins join Nancy Grace to discuss the case. Crime Stories can also be heard each day on SiriusXM's ch. 132.
